name: emoji_stealer
description: This cog lets you steal emojis from any server and add them to yours. Use !steal <emoji> [name]
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any user data.
install_msg: Thanks for installing emoji_stealer! Use !steal <:emoji:ID> [name] to import emojis from other servers.
author: ThatGirl-me
